        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "a hundred talents — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Which at f4,500 per talent, make f450,000 sterling. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Also twenty basins of gold of a thousand drachms — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "About f1,000 sterling value. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And two vessels of fine copper ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
